titles.title: To suspend temporarily the duty on Cibacron Brilliant Blue FN-G.

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on Ways and Means.
Referred to the Subcommittee on Trade.

committee.name: House Committee on Ways and Means

bill.summary: 6/10/1999--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend, through December 31, 2003, the duty on 4, 11- triphenodioxazinedisulfonic acid, 6,13-dichloro-3, 10-bis((2-((-((4- fluoro-6-((2-sulfophenyl) amino)-1,3,5-triazin-2-yl) amino) propyl) amino)- lithium sodium salt (Cibacron Brilliant Blue FN-G).
